<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>战区</title><link>https://www.twz.com</link><description>防御世界的强大进攻。</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 16:00:19 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>波音公司新型更大的“幽灵蝙蝠”可在内部携带 AIM-120 AMRAAM</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/boeings-new-larger-ghost-bat-can-carry-aim-120-amraams-internally</link><description>&lt;p&gt;隐形幽灵蝙蝠正在进入第三次迭代，拥有更大的翅膀、更强的力量和内部武器舱。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/boeings-new-larger-ghost-bat-can-carry-aim-120-amraams-internally"&gt;波音公司新型大型幽灵蝙蝠可在内部携带 AIM-120 AMRAAM 的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 21:12:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/boeings-new-larger-ghost-bat-can-carry-aim-120-amraams-internally</guid></item><item><title>隔夜袭击破坏美伊停火（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/overnight-attacks-rattle-u-s-iran-ceasefire</link><description>&lt;p&gt;美国和伊朗之间的最新一轮针锋相对的袭击是自4月8日达成停火以来最严重的袭击之一。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/overnight-attacks-rattle-u-s-iran-ceasefire"&gt;隔夜袭击扰乱美伊停火（更新）&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 20:13:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/overnight-attacks-rattle-u-s-iran-ceasefire</guid></item><item><title>这架神秘的空军 737 即将成为 NASA 的下一个“呕吐彗星”吗？</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/is-this-secretive-air-force-737-about-to-become-nasas-next-vomit-comet</link><description>&lt;p&gt;NASA 希望聘请一家非常专业的公司来看看“机密”空军 737 是否可以用作低重力工作的测试平台。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;这篇文章&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/is-this-secretive-air-force-737-about-to-become-nasas-next-vomit-comet"&gt;这架神秘的空军 737 即将成为 NASA 的下一个“呕吐彗星”吗？&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 18:47:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/is-this-secretive-air-force-737-about-to-become-nasas-next-vomit-comet</guid></item><item><title>德国 Cobra 600 是一款喷气动力拦截无人机，可发射 IRIS-T 导弹</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/germanys-cobra-600-is-a-jet-powered-interceptor-drone-that-slings-an-iris-t-missile</link><description>&lt;p&gt;眼镜蛇 600 携带导弹距离跑道发射点数百英里，扩大了地对空导弹电池的射程。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/germanys-cobra-600-is-a-jet-powered-interceptor-drone-that-slings-an-iris-t-missile"&gt;德国的 Cobra 600 是一款可发射 IRIS-T 导弹的喷气动力拦截无人机，&lt;/a&gt;该帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 16:49:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/germanys-cobra-600-is-a-jet-powered-interceptor-drone-that-slings-an-iris-t-missile</guid></item><item><title>AH-64阿帕奇被伊朗击落，美国将进行报复：特朗普（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/ah-64-apache-shot-down-by-iran-u-s-will-retaliate-trump</link><description>&lt;p&gt;AH-64 坠入阿曼湾，机组人员被无人船救起，现在特朗普称这是由于敌人的行动。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/ah-64-apache-shot-down-by-iran-u-s-will-retaliate-trump"&gt;伊朗击落 AH-64 阿帕奇后，美国将进行报复：特朗普（更新）&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jun 2026 22:25:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/ah-64-apache-shot-down-by-iran-u-s-will-retaliate-trump</guid></item><item><title>这是将被击落的阿帕奇船员从阿曼湾救出的海盗船无人机船</title><link>https://www.twz.com/sea/this-is-the-corsair-drone-boat-that-plucked-the-downed-apache-crew-out-of-the-gulf-of-oman</link><description>&lt;p&gt;美国海军在中东的顶级无人机特遣部队今年三月才开始操作海盗船无人水面舰艇。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;这篇文章&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/sea/this-is-the-corsair-drone-boat-that-plucked-the-downed-apache-crew-out-of-the-gulf-of-oman"&gt;“这是从阿曼湾救出被击落的阿帕奇船员的海盗船无人机船”&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jun 2026 19:40:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/sea/this-is-the-corsair-drone-boat-that-plucked-the-downed-apache-crew-out-of-the-gulf-of-oman</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰人工智能无人机攻击俄罗斯后勤系统的内幕</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/inside-ukraines-ai-enabled-drone-campaign-targeting-russian-logistics-deep-behind-the-lines</link><description>&lt;p&gt;一名负责“中程”无人机行动的军官对无人机对俄罗斯后勤中心的打击提供了前所未有的见解。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/inside-ukraines-ai-enabled-drone-campaign-targeting-russian-logistics-deep-behind-the-lines"&gt;乌克兰人工智能无人机行动深入后方，瞄准俄罗斯后勤保障的&lt;/a&gt;帖子首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;“战区”&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jun 2026 19:30:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/inside-ukraines-ai-enabled-drone-campaign-targeting-russian-logistics-deep-behind-the-lines</guid></item><item><title>Ravenstorm 是空中客车公司全新战斗无人机产品组合的核心</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/ravenstorm-at-the-center-of-airbuss-new-combat-drone-portfolio</link><description>&lt;p&gt;随着欧洲下一代旗舰战斗机的开发，空中客车公司在无人驾驶协作战斗机上投入了大量资金。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/ravenstorm-at-the-center-of-airbuss-new-combat-drone-portfolio"&gt;《Ravenstorm At the Center of Airbus&amp;#39;s New Combat Drone Portfolio》&lt;/a&gt;一文首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jun 2026 18:05:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/ravenstorm-at-the-center-of-airbuss-new-combat-drone-portfolio</guid></item><item><title>AH-64 阿帕奇船员在霍尔木兹海峡附近坠落后被无人机船救起（更新）</title><link>https://www.twz.com/news-features/ah-64-apache-crew-rescued-by-drone-boat-after-going-down-near-strait-of-hormuz</link><description>&lt;p&gt;这是已知的首次使用无人水面舰艇来营救坠落的机组人员，也是未来发展的重要标志。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/news-features/ah-64-apache-crew-rescued-by-drone-boat-after-going-down-near-strait-of-hormuz"&gt;AH-64 阿帕奇机组人员在霍尔木兹海峡附近坠落后被无人机救起（更新）后&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;战区&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jun 2026 13:29:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/news-features/ah-64-apache-crew-rescued-by-drone-boat-after-going-down-near-strait-of-hormuz</guid></item><item><title>VC-25B 空军一号“桥梁”飞机现在涂上了特朗普喜欢的红、白、蓝油漆</title><link>https://www.twz.com/air/vc-25b-air-force-one-bridge-aircraft-now-wears-trumps-preferred-red-white-and-blue-paint-job</link><description>&lt;p&gt;VC-25B“桥”喷气式飞机也在今年夏天正式首次亮相之前进行最后一轮改装。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href="https://www.twz.com/air/vc-25b-air-force-one-bridge-aircraft-now-wears-trumps-preferred-red-white-and-blue-paint-job"&gt;VC-25B 后的空军一号“桥梁”飞机现在涂上了特朗普喜欢的红、白、蓝油漆，&lt;/a&gt;首先出现在&lt;a href="https://www.twz.com"&gt;《战区》&lt;/a&gt;上。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jun 2026 01:09:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.twz.com/air/vc-25b-air-force-one-bridge-aircraft-now-wears-trumps-preferred-red-white-and-blue-paint-job</guid></item></channel></rss>